CSAs are healthy for the local economy, the land, the community, and you.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><strong>Join today.<\/strong>\u00a0The CSA starts in May. Members are welcome through the middle of July.\u00a0 Fees will be prorated.<\/p>\n<p>Please browse our site to learn more, or contact us at:\u00a0<a href=\"mailto:irvingtonagriculture@gmail.com\">IrvingtonAgriculture@gmail.com<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_3&#8243;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;http:\/\/irvingtoncsa.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/Blackberries.jpg&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;3.0.98&#8243;]<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_image][et_pb_cta title=&#8221;Join us!&#8221; button_url=&#8221;http:\/\/irvingtonagriculture@gmail.com&#8221; background_color=&#8221;#621263&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;3.0.98&#8243;]<\/p>\n<p>irvingtonagriculture@gmail.com<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_cta][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[et_pb_section bb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;3.0.47&#8243;][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;3.0.47&#8243; background_size=&#8221;initial&#8221; background_position=&#8221;top_left&#8221; background_repeat=&#8221;repeat&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;2_3&#8243;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;3.0.98&#8243;] Why join a CSA? Know where your food comes from.Your produce comes directly from the farmer and is grown locally using sustainable non-chemical farming methods. Support small local farming.Gives local economy a boost and supports the farming families. \u00a0Get more bang for your buck.You&#8217;re not paying [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_et_pb_use_builder":"on","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-109","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"jet